flowchart TD
    A[cargo profile-build] --> B[Set RUSTC_WRAPPER]
    B --> C[cargo build]
    C --> D{For each crate}
    D --> E[rustc-wrapper]
    E --> F{Target crate?}
    F -->|No| G[Pass through to rustc]
    F -->|Yes| H[Emit LLVM IR]
    H --> I[Instrument IR]
    I --> J[Compile with clang/llc]
    J --> K[Link with runtime]
    K --> L[Instrumented binary]
